Key Match Events: South Africa lost the crucial make or break match at the Adelaide Oval to go down to ‘minnows’ Netherlands by 13 runs.
Pre-Game Insights: A win here would have meant the Proteas are through to the semi-finals.
In the unlikely scenario of their defeat, they will have to pack their bags for home.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This victory propelled India into the semi-finals.
